title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 24 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 24 2021
description:
Guest James Miervaldis of No One Left Behind discussed the situation in Afghanistan and helping foreign interpreters. What can we do to help? LSU season ticket holders call in to discuss the new vaccine mandates. Can Democrats survive a Gavin Newsom recall election? California police find hundreds of recall ballots, guns, and drugs inside sleeping man's car. Psaki uses her own kids as props to call for mask mandates.
